ISLAMABAD, Jan 14 (APP): Minister for Information and Broadcasting Chaudhry Fawad Hussain on Friday said thatin line with new National Security Policy through which Pakistan declared geoeconomics as core of national security doctrine, the Government has decided to allow permanent residency scheme for foreign nationals.
In a tweet he said that the new policy allows foreigners to get permanent resident status in lieu of investment in Pakistan.
